C.b4K=new B.o("A text control that makes suggestions to users as they type. The app is notified when text has been changed by the user and is responsible for providing relevant suggestions for this control to display.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
C.b4R=new B.o("Use a TimePicker to let users set a time in your app, for example to set a reminder. The TimePicker displays three controls for hour, minute, and AM/PM. These controls are easy to use with touch or mouse, and they can be styled and configured in several different ways.\n\nThe entry point displays the chosen time, and when the user selects the entry point, a picker surface expands vertically from the middle for the user to make a selection. The time picker overlays other UI; it doesn't push other UI out of the way.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
